Rowdy Wolf:




Rowdy Wolf watched Zyber's body movements every second. But calmness 
returned to him when she asked to return with him to his den. He grinned and 
nodded slowly to her. "Yes you may," he replied to her. "You are always 
welcome." He wagged his tail and turned his hind-quarters to her, ready to 
head back to his cave.
